{"tid":1777802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【打氣】記唔記得香港人有幾勁？","createTime":"2019-12-10T13:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T04:49:19.000Z","uid":329034,"like":153,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"81445edb3930f40c0abe23eb20943143994824f0","tid":1777802,"uid":329034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:13:44.000Z","msg":"第六個月喇，係咪好攰呢？<br />\n<br />\n老實講，係咪開始唔記得6月嘅情況呢<br />\n等我提下大家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地創造咗自己嘅手語<br />\n<br />\n我地遊行會買一堆物資送去前線<br />\n堆滿哂成條夏慤道<br />\n<br />\n我地由pp傳頭盔去政總只係用緊幾十秒<br />\n<br />\n我地分紅海讓路比救護車只係幾秒嘅事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0KrxSu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0KrxSu.png&h=ba4ce7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsAycSD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsAycSD.png&h=cfc1cd41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0vycSJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0vycSJ.png&h=6d0a9cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucdWU6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucdWU6b.png&h=1fdf1b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w28zGMk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw28zGMk.png&h=1036f3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uKnXEx7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuKnXEx7.png&h=a3553bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JaHArdg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJaHArdg.png&h=607cb9f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVEOMdo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVEOMdo.png&h=7ddc7ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一路以嚟，我地未退後過<br />\n經歷咗612 721 831 101 <br />\n係咪覺得好灰心 係咪覺得好冇希望<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">但係大家係咪唔記得咗 我地未輸㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n我覺得香港人係世界上最勁嘅民族<br />\n我知道我地一定會贏嘅<br />\n<br />\n當你身邊嘅朋友行得好攰嘅時候 <br />\n不妨圍爐傾下計 比啲信心大家<br />\n可能有好多人覺得好絕望 覺得會輸 <br />\n<br />\n但唔好唔記得 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">覺得為時已晚的時候，恰恰是最早的時候。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n成日都話社運人士同公義會遲到<br />\n的確我地係遲咗醒覺 <br />\n咁但係黎明一定會嚟㗎嘛<br />\n鼓勵返身邊戰友 一齊返嚟打返呢場自由之戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為香港人咩都做得到</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8185d92aa5c2ccd24ebd972d5de8fe36dd4bc9","tid":1777802,"uid":317979,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ThXMxUk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThXMxUk.gif&h=214a7d87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5d5801c6c60585326bcc6b941754b813fdda7ed","tid":1777802,"uid":317979,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ou1xtsY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOu1xtsY.jpg&h=52c0c38a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1302091ded97ce4d52bcdc3e10b51db28b813a7","tid":1777802,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7270803ccb0fa361b166bc7252385ca1a00096d","tid":1777802,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:25:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e42275f68f943bb8cb87b58ef1eea8bbb0ff19ff